text: Mir Majedur Rahman is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Tangail-5. ==Career== Rahman was elected to parliament from Tangail-5 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Mir Majedur Rahman
